    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/lac/fbh/6045472908.html"></div>
        </div>
Kronfli Brothers Group, owners of Bacaro LA, Nature's Brew, Bacari PDR, Bacari GDL, and Kronfli Bros products, is currently seeking experienced and qualified candidates to fill the full-time Junior Sous Chef position at Bacaro LA, our high volume, young, fun, energetic restaurant. Our chef-driven, creative cicchetti-style menu is influenced by Mediterranean cuisines, and our service is fast-paced and fun. <br>
<br>
A qualified candidate has youthful energy and at least two years minimum of kitchen and cooking experience. Being fluent in both English and Spanish is a big plus as well. <br>
<br>
You should have an impeccable attention to detail, a passion for food and hospitality, a strong grasp on inventory and cost control, and a knack for leading your fellow kitchen team members. <br>
<br>
Kronfli Bros group is also growing quickly, so you must be willing and able to move and lead kitchens at new locations as we open them around the greater Los Angeles area in the near future. There is always opportunity to grow within the company.<br>
<br>
This position pays a guaranteed $38,000 annually, plus tips that average about $500/month, with opportunity to earn benefits within the first year. We are looking for long term, career driven candidates that are looking to grow with us as the company expands.<br>
<br>
The current Bacaro LA team is a close-knit friendly staff, and we are looking for a Junior Sous Chef to join the family!<br>
<br>
Please send along a resume and an introduction to yourself, and we'll be in touch soon to set up a time for an interview!    </section>

